reviews.text:
A good choice of Japanese restaurant. The skill and food quality is good. BBQ is tasty but not salty and recommend BBQ eel. Light grill salmon is a good balance of grill and fresh with a taste of fruit source. 
Another recommendation is the shrimp pancake although it's in Korean style.

Great experience of japanese dining. Service was great and the waiters are very polite. Waiting time for the dishes are not too long. Better to book on weekends as it is very full most of the time during peak hours. Only thing stopping me from rating it a 5 star is that when it's peak hour, the grilling smoke takes over the restaurant and the ventilation system isn't too great.
Excellent food. Great service. Interesting decor. Will definitely visit again.
Not expensive if no sashimi
Great food and good place for hanging out with friends! Packed even on a Thursday night. Book ahead.

reviews.text: 舒適的日本菜，招牌玉子燒無驚喜，跟午餐MOKA咖啡不錯，可以再試！

A good choice of Japanese restaurant. The skill and food quality is good. BBQ is tasty but not salty and recommend BBQ eel. Light grill salmon is a good balance of grill and fresh with a taste of fruit source. 
Another recommendation is the shrimp pancake although it's in Korean style.
平日享受高C/P值既午餐已經好滿足，今晚晚餐雖然貴少少，不過都食得好舒服。除左玉子燒必食外，明太子抄豚肉&🦀籽窩飯更有驚喜！
泰國飲品，好飲。但不可少冰，整杯冰！
地方整潔，限時個半小時進餐，不能電話訂坐。
